msgctxt "3827	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Christmas is coming up soon. It'd be good to do something for the kids. Maybe I'll ask Wada-san at the office for advice. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3950	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Wada-san saw right through me. I guess I'll try and do what I can. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4018	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Izumi's present using the ATM. 5,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4098	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Shiro's present using the ATM. 5,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4178	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Eri's present using the ATM. 8,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4256	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Riona's present using the ATM. 6,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4336	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Mitsuo's present using the ATM. 6,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4417	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Koji's present using the ATM. 10,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4497	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Taichi's present using the ATM. 10,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4579	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll send money for Ayako's present using the ATM. 20,000 yen should be enough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4660	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I wonder if this will cheer the kids up. Heh, I'm probably just doing it to feel better about myself. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4763	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I've finished sending the eight kids money. I hope they have a good Christmas even without me there. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4865	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There was apparently a taxi with its emergency light triggered on Nagasu Boulevard. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4950	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The taxi just sped off all of a sudden. It looked like it was heading north along Nagasu Boulevard. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5051	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It looks like the taxi is headed toward Suzukake Lane. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5107	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It looks like the taxi went further south from Suzukake Lane. Maybe I should head to Fukuhaku Street. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5210	EXPLANATION"
msgid "This is the guy behind it all! I've got to save the driver. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5271	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It looks like we both had it wrong. Well, at least the misunderstanding is sorted out now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5363	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Kiyokawa is having a mixer party at Motsunabe Kaede. I want to help out if I can. Maybe they're still waiting outside. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5483	EXPLANATION"
msgid "We made it through that mixer party. It didn't turn out as well as it could have, but those two seemed to be okay. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5599	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I have to save that kidnapped kid! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5635	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I couldn't catch the kidnapper, but at least the kid is safe now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5702	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'm glad I caught up to that kidnapper. It's a relief to know the kid is safe now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5786	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That was no ordinary dog howl. I think it was coming from behind the toilets next to the river. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5883	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I guess idiots who gang up and prey upon the weak can be found anywhere. I think they need a little wake-up call. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5998	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I need to bring Haruka's father to where she is. He should be at Café Portugal on Nagasu Boulevard. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6100	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Who'd stoop to taking a young girl hostage? These guys are a lost cause. Time to make them pay. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6197	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It was good to see Haruka and her father patch things up. I wish I could see my Haruka... "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6288	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I have to do something about the chief's computer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6339	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like that messed it up badly. I probably should have stopped the chief."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6417	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'm glad it wasn't anything too serious. I made the right call stopping the chief. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6501	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Kudarizaka was looking for someone to stand in for him in a movie. I might still find him on Chikuzengawa Street. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6616	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I've got to defeat the zombies just like the script says. It's kind of tricky, though. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6704	EXPLANATION"
msgid "They want me fight this horde of zombies? These movie actors have a rough job. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6784	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Time for the climactic scene of the movie. Hopefully I can pack plenty of action into it. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6875	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I guess I didn't make a very good stand-in actor. The acting business is pretty tough. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6963	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It looks like I did an okay job filling in on the movie. This acting business is a lot tougher than I imagined."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7075	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yuya is the last person I expected to see in Nagasugai. Luckily, my true identity wasn't exposed to Muramatsu-san. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7191	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It sounds like Yuya has his fair share of troubles, too. I hope things go well for him no matter what he decides. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7306	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I got an email from Yuya. Apparently he got a job as a waiter at a cabaret club called La Seine. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7404	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yuya seemed to be doing well at that cabaret club. I'll have to check in on him again sometime. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7501	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I wonder how Yuya is doing. Maybe I'll go see him at La Seine. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7565	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Heh. Yuya has that same old spark in his eyes again now. I'll give him a hand with these yakuza. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7663	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I know you still have things on your mind, Yuya, but good luck back at Stardust. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7745	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Maybe a new neighbor came to introduce themselves? I pretended I was out, but I should say hi if they come back. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7859	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It's one of those pushy newspaper salesmen. I think I'll rough him up a little to teach him a lesson. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7962	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It was too much trouble to talk him around, so I signed up for a newspaper subscription. Talk about a pushy salesman. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8081	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That newspaper salesman was about as obnoxious as they come, but I think he'll change his tune now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8182	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A fisherman invited me to do some river fishing. He's toward the north end of Chikuzengawa Street. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8282	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It's sea fishing this time. That could be fun. I can meet him toward the north end of Chikuzengawa Street again. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8396	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So Kimura-san is the Tuna King, huh? That Dragon Seafood Bowl tasted incredible. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8478	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The Spangled Meteor? What sort of girl drives a car like that? "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8542	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That Nanami girl had heard rumors about me. I wonder if she has something to do with the Spangled Meteor? "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8649	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I got a challenge from the Spangled Meteor. The driver seems to know me, so maybe it really is Nanami. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8753	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I got a challenge from the Spangled Meteor. I lost the last race, but this time I think I can win and unmask them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8868	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The Spangled Meteor is Rena Nanami. She's a good woman who understands the importance of being honest with herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8984	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So this guy's name is Hors d'Oeuvre Morosawa? He's a little out of control. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9061	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I could join him in the ring if I had something to hide my face with. Did I have anything like that at my apartment? "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9179	EXPLANATION"
msgid "With the dragon mask, I can take part in the bout with Morosawa. I'll go home to prepare then head to Ose Bridge. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9294	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll make Hors d'Oeuvre Morosawa's retirement fight a fitting end to his career. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9376	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Who knew that dragon mask would come in handy? I think Morosawa got the closure he was looking for. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9477	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That student who lost his answer booklet looked pretty stressed out. I wonder if he's still at Ose Bridge. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9585	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I think that student learned something more important than the answers to his test. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9670	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A food stall owner wanted me to help get his stall in place. He's probably still on Meisei Street."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9769	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Unless I get that poor guy's food stall in place soon, he won't be able to open on time. I'd better hurry up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9879	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I lugged the food stall over, but it got a bit damaged. At least his patrons won't miss out on their food."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9986	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I lugged the food stall over in one piece. Now his patrons won't have to wait for their food."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10080	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It sounds like this place is pretty deep in debt. I should ask for more details in case I can help out. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10185	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Tatsuya is scouring the country for ideas to use in his new creations. Once he's done, he might be able to lend a hand. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10306	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Tatsuya said he was at Theater Square. I should go and meet him there. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10378	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I bet Tatsuya can come up with plenty of other masterpiece dishes in the future. I hope he keeps it up. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10483	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Mack Shinozuka... I met him in Kamurocho before. He seems to be traveling the world and taking photos again. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10593	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Revelations, huh? I guess I'll let Mack know if I capture any moments that strike me as special. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10691	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That food stall ramen I had with the chief tasted great. When I get a chance, I want to go and try it again. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10801	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Cooking noodles is more hectic than I thought. The guy looked happy, so maybe I'll go help out again sometime. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10913	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I got a challenge from the Amon Clan. Once we're all ready, their messenger outside New Serena will take us where they are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11037	EXPLANATION"
msgid "We have to finish things with the Amon Clan. I need to make sure we all get back alive. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11126	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I guess there's no end in sight for our struggle with the Amon Clan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11197	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Those hostesses were talkin' about Himura near Rose Hip."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11254	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Could be others 'round here who knew Himura. Gotta be a lot of foot traffic passing through the arcade area. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11364	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Another one of those arms deals Himura was talkin' about in the slammer could be goin' down. Probably in Ramen Village. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11485	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's supposed to be an arms deal at the plaza in Ramen Village. Cops'll be there, but I better go for a look. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11599	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Ain't every day I end up protectin' cops from the mafia. Still, I'll pay back the debt I owe, Himura! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11702	EXPLANATION"
msgid "For better or worse, Himura's a show-off. I got taken in hook, line, and sinker. It was still fun, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11809	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That guy's three sheets to the wind. Better steer clear of him. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11874	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That old guy in Ambitious was hammered. Maybe I oughta hear him out at least. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11953	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Araseki-han ran off after the bag snatcher! They were headed towards Nakatsuki Street. I better go after 'em. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12064	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Losers with no dreams ain't got a right to look down on Araseki-han. I'll show 'em the error of their ways. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12173	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So Araseki-han was chasin' old Oshima, huh? I better watch my step next time I see him. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12262	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like Sodachi's been workin' on his skills. Let's see how far he's come. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12341	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like Sodachi's been workin' on his skills. Let's see how far he's come. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12420	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Sounds like Sodachi's trainin' his heart out. Hope he keeps makin' more progress. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12503	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Sounds like Sodachi's in some kinda trouble! Better head to the dojo right now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12584	EXPLANATION"
msgid "This place is precious to us. No way I'm gonna let these guys ruin that! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12658	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Keep holdin' down the fort for us, Sodachi. That place is special to us all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12735	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Who'd wanna harm Santa? I might go and help out later. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12791	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Santa hunters? What's wrong with these guys? I better track 'em down and give 'em a talking-to. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12888	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Don't tell me these guys are huntin' down Santas! Guess I'm gonna have to turn tail and run. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12982	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Santa hunters, huh? I might help out if I get the chance. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13041	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So these're the Santa hunters. Time to give 'em a piece of my mind. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13110	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Guess that settles that. I could get used to bein' Santa. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13169	EXPLANATION"
msgid "They need me to check where each of the snow sculptures are at. Guess I could pitch in for the sake of the festival. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13287	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I was supposed to check where the snow sculptures are at. Gotta tell the guy on the west side of the snow festival. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13404	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like I messed up the location of the snow sculptures. Better check one more time and go tell that guy again. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13520	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like I messed up the location of the snow sculptures. The snow festival's gonna be fun. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13615	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like I got the snow sculpture locations right. I'm really lookin' forward to the snow festival. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13718	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Masao said he was headed to Tsukimino. Hope his mom at the village'll be okay. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13798	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta deliver this letter to Masao that his mom gave me. Think he was workin' at a place called Apocalypse. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13907	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's a place called Apocalypse near Rose Hip. Gotta deliver this letter to Masao that his mom gave me. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14014	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like Masao got set up by that club. He ain't there anymore, so where's he at now? "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14103	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Looks like Masao's learnin' a few lessons about life. Now I gotta teach these guys a lesson as well! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14205	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Ya only learn to appreciate parents after ya leave home. Never give up, Masao. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14285	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That girl had a hankerin' for lamb barbecue so bad she damn near starved herself for it. Had me worried for nothin'. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14403	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That barbecue girl ran off like the wind. She ain't actually gonna go up the mountain, is she? "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14499	EXPLANATION"
msgid "From the sound of things at the village, that girl really did head up the mountain! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14584	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That barbecue girl actually made it up the mountain. I better take her down to safety. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14672	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Made it off the mountain by the skin of our teeth. Hope that girl's gonna be okay. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14756	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta hand it to that barbecue girl, she's sure dedicated. Gotta hunt a deer to fill her belly up. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14856	EXPLANATION"
msgid "What kinda girl goes that far for a meal? You're something else, Mami Yamashita. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14938	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Anti-cold gear, huh? Sounds fishy to me. Wonder if that researcher's still on Tsukasa Street. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15033	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So much for the ultimate anti-cold gear! Gotta put this fire out with a fire extinguisher! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15125	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That anti-cold gear was some bullshit all right. Still, I guess I don't feel cold anymore. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15217	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Some kinda accident outside Northern Lane? Maybe I oughta check it out. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15290	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Wasn't expectin' to face off with a bear here in town. Better take care of it before someone gets hurt. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15395	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Lucky for me, that bear was pretty small. Nobody ended up gettin' hurt. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15468	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Wonder if that little match girl's still out in front of Ambitious. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15537	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Hope that match girl's okay. Maybe I'll go look out in front of Ambitious. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15613	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta get some nourishin' food to her. Hang in there, little match girl. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15687	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The match girl's lookin' much better now. Wish I could help her out with her matches. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15774	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I oughta help the poor girl sell some matches. I'll try talkin' to some likely buyers. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15862	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So I reminded her of her dad, huh? That's not a bad feeling, I guess. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15933	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I should bring that guy behind Don Quijote some hot food. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15992	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Good to see him perkin' up. Hope he makes it to Tokyo all right. "
