msgid "Damn it. I got spotted while I was following him. There goes my chance at some quick cash. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32324	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Damn it. I got spotted while I was following him. There goes my chance at some quick cash. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32416	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I managed to stay on his tail! Boy, this is tough work. That earned me some quick cash, though! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32513	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Someone's giving a speech over by the oval stage. They look a bit troubled. Maybe I'll go and say hi. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32616	EXPLANATION"
msgid "So the manager of Shachoko is getting into politics, huh? Hopefully he finds someone to do an endorsement speech. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32731	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I wonder if the Shachoko manager found someone to give a speech for him. He was over by the oval stage. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32836	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Hardly anyone paid any attention. I guess I let the manager down. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32903	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That seemed to go well. The manager has a lot more support than he thought. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32980	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Part time work at a convenience store, huh? I guess I could try that when I have some time. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33073	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I couldn't catch the shoplifter in the end. No way they'll let me take expired lunches home now. "
msgstr ""

