msgid "I managed to catch that shoplifter. Maybe this means more expired lunches for me! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33254	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It's good to see someone taking an interest in baseball. I'll give him a few pointers when I get a chance. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33362	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That wasn't the greatest display of my ability. If I see him around again, I'll show him the proper way to do it. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33477	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Now it's up to him to follow through. I might come and see how he's doing later. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33559	EXPLANATION"
msgid "What's with that chicken? I guess I'll try to catch it and get the reward! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33635	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I didn't catch it myself, but I still got the reward. Cochin racing, huh? I might try it out when I get a chance. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33750	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I caught the chicken and received the reward! Cochin racing, huh? I might try it out when I get a chance. "
msgstr ""

